title: Bloomberg Businessweek Weekend - February 16th, 2019
itunes:title: Bloomberg Businessweek Weekend - February 16th, 2019
description:
Hosted by Carol Massar and Jason Kelly.

Featuring:

-Bret Begun on the Real Estate Double Issue

-Stephen Gandel details why private equity likes the look of Blackstone’s real estate model

-Tom Leighton, Akamai CEO, describes his company’s next big bet...on Blockchain

-Lonne Joffe, Insight Venture Partners Managing Director, explains how some of the smartest machines around are actually job-creators.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
